		  - 5.25 inch disk drive
		  - 300 rotation per minute (RPM)
		  - 125 or 250 kBit/s transfere rate
		  - FM or MFM operation (SD/DD)
		  - 96 tracks per inch (TPI)
		  - 80 tracks per side
		  - single side
		  - max. 400 kB

		This drive is compatible to the original TEAC floppy disk
